@@TJvCustomHTListBox.HideSel
Summary
  Influences redrawing of the control following changes in the focused selection.
Description
  HideSel is a Boolean property that influences redrawing of the control following changes in the
  focused selection. Changing the value of the HideSel property force the control to be redrawn by
